Phn tch cc yu t nh hng n xp hng ca ng dng trn google play store

  • Nhom thc hin
    • Nguyn Ngoc Hoa - 18133014
    • L inh Khang - 18133021
    • Vo Thi Thanh Ngn - 18133033
  • Thi gian thc hin: 17-27/1/2021

Gii thiu

  • Ngun d liu: https://www.kaggle.com/lava18/google-play-store-apps
  • Phn tich tp d liu va rut ra thng tin hu ich cho nhng nha phat trin ng dung Android

  • M ta cac bin

Cu hoi phn tich

    1. Danh mc(Loai) ng dng ca hng Google Play no c xp hng cao nht?
    1. Liu xp hang cua mt ng dung khng bi han ch tui co khac bit vi mt ng dung bi han ch tui hay khng?
    1. C s khc bit ng k v xp hng gia ng dng ca hng Google Play tr ph hay min ph khng?

Hiu van

  • Xem lt qua d liu
  • Tra li s b cac cu hoi

Thit k nghin cu

  • Nghin cu nay la nghin cu quan sat(observational study)
  • Phng phap chon mu:Simple random sampling

Suy ngm v cu hoi

  • Tra li mt cach chu quan(theo trc giac) cac cu hoi
  • Lin h thc t

Kt qua at c

  • ANOVA F-test cung cp bng chng thng k kt lun rng cac danh muc ng dung khac nhau co xp hang khac nhau va ng dung giao duc co ve nh la co rating cao nht.
  • two sample t-test chi ra rng co s khac bit ro rang v rating gia ng dung bi han ch tui va ng dung khng bi han ch tui. Tuy nhin phan oan chu quan cua chung ta la sai.
  • two sample t-test chi ra rng co s khac bit ro rang v rating gia ng dung tra tin va min phi cu th hn la ng dung tra tin co rating cao hn. iu o hoan toan khp vi d oan cua chung ta.

Tng kt

  • Co th a ra mt s gi y chung cho nha phat trin v ni dung lam ngi dung hai long, tuy nhin vic ng dung phat trin ra sao con tuy thuc vao xu hng hin tai.
  • Nhc im cua bai phn tich:
    • Nghin cu nay la mt nghin cu quan sat nn khng th a ra cac kt lun nhn qua nhm giup cho ngi phat trin hiu hn va co th d oan c thi trng tng lai.
    • Vic thu thp d liu cua toan b ng dung trn CH Play gn nh la iu khng th vi th tinh ngu nhin cua mu khng c am bao, rt kho ta a ra kt lun cho toan b cac ng dung trn CH Play.
    • Thi gian va kin thc han hep, khng tranh khoi sai sot trong qua trinh thc hin.
